The paper is about developing software effort estimation models using artificial neural networks, which is a topic related to software engineering (cs.SE). The use of artificial neural networks also falls under the categories of artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), and neural networks (cs.NE). Additionally, the paper discusses the comparison of different neural network models, which can be considered as a system analysis and control (cs.SY) aspect.
